reviewText: Good to watch long forgotten program.
I love every jerry lewis thing all I do on amazon is order jerry lewis

I like Jerry Lewis and wanted to see this material...As an adult I found the material to be very corny, cheesy whatever word you want to use, but my girlfriends two daughters one 7 and one 9 loved it..It is zany..I think every bucked tooth character Jerry ever created is on this disk...

I like Jerry Lewis, but this collection is just bad, awful, or any other negative word you can think of?!!! If this collection are "Fan Favorites", I really would hate to see the ones that weren't favorites!!!!!!!!!!!
